code: @Test public void noStackTrace() {     String s = this.converter.convert(this.event).     assertThat(s).isEqualTo(""). }

@Test public void withStackTrace() {     this.event.setThrowableProxy(new ThrowableProxy(new RuntimeException())).     String s = this.converter.convert(this.event).     assertThat(s).startsWith(System.lineSeparator()).endsWith(System.lineSeparator()). }
